org.xadisk.additional
Class XAFileOutputStreamWrapper

java.lang.Object
  java.io.OutputStream
      org.xadisk.additional.XAFileOutputStreamWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, Flushable
public class XAFileOutputStreamWrapper
extends OutputStream

This class acts as a wrapper around the XAFileOutputStream for the purpose of providing the standard OutputStream implementation (because XAFileOutputStream itself does not extend the OutputStream).

Since:
1.0
